transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Haan ji Rinku madam.
Customer: Haan. Ji madam Prashant baat kar raha hun IndiaMART se senior manager. Prashant ji aapko hi phone kar rahi thi main good morning aaj aapne meeting rakhne bola tha aapne aapne whatsapp bhi nahi kiya link bhi nahi share kiya. 
Executive: Maine aapko whatsapp nahi kiya tha maine us din?
Customer: Nahi nahi kiya. Aapna call kiya tha?
Customer: Nahi kiya. Bina whatsapp bina whatsapp kiye maine aapko.
Customer: Haan. Uh ye nahi kiya na sir ye number aapne kaunse number pe kiya jis se baat ho rahi hai us pe kiya kya?
Executive: Uh jis number se baat ho rahi hai usi number pe kiya tha na.
Customer: Nahi nahi to ye number pe whatsapp nahi chal raha na maine aapko another number diya tha mera personal number.
Executive: Ye 99 wala number hai na last mein 099 wala. Ye kya bol rahe hai aap mujhe number bataiye.
Customer: 766
Executive: Ji?
Customer: 766
Executive: Just one minute.
Customer: Uh seven triple six triple six double eight.
Customer: Triple eight.
Customer: 886548
Executive: Ek minute seven ke baad triple six bola tha aapne right?
Customer: Right.
Executive: Uske baad double eight hai ya triple eight hai?
Customer: Double eight hai.
Executive: Double eight 65
Customer: 65 48
Executive: 48
Customer: Haan ye number pe jara link share kare whatsapp kare na to mere seniors ko bhi main share kar deti hun aur aap schedule bhi karenge na to like second half week mein hi kariye.
Executive: Aap jab bhi aapko lage like ki aap available hai na aap mujhe call kar sakti hai.
Customer: Tab link to share kar dijiye sir main bata dungi.
Executive: Nahi link main tabhi generate kar dunga na within seconds link generate ho jata hai. Achcha hai. Nahi kyunki aap mujhe bata dete to main mere mein seniors ko bhej deti thi na second half mein koi bhi time pe kariye ki wo log available hi hai second half mein.
Executive: Ye dekhiye maine apna jo number hai na. Bhej diya. Theek hai?
Customer: Aapne bheja? Haan aaya message.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai.
Customer: Theek hai aap send kar dijiye abhi aapko. Sure theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai. Okay okay. Thank you.
summary:
Concerns:

- Meeting link not shared by executive.

- Wants the link to be shared on WhatsApp.

- Wants meeting in the second half of the week.



Resolution:

- Executive took the correct WhatsApp number.

- Executive sent the WhatsApp message.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- meeting, whatsapp, link, schedule
